{"tid":1703031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有班醫護驚再有手足失救拍埋FA教學片，竟然無人睇","createTime":"2019-11-10T05:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T18:47:00.000Z","uid":281252,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"074484a46bba79339045664e7d1c2c8df54f557b","tid":1703031,"uid":281252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T05:21:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見到條片得幾百個View，大家係咪唔想救手足啦？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔一定要係，每個人都要睇要學，每多一個人睇到學識就可以幫手足爭取多一點生存機會。<br />\n<br />\n黑警愈嚟愈癲，傷者隨時都會喺身邊出現，無FA喺現場係咪就唔救由得佢死？花幾分鐘時間睇晒佢，你永都都唔知幾時有用。<br />\n<br />\n有班前線醫護人員擔心佢地即使做FA都救唔晒所有手足，走咗去拍片教大家，希望可以救得一個多一個。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋唔想再失去任何一個手足。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝<br />\n衝衝子 FA 升級攻略YouTube Channel：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEjBVqymzca1SIn3a5BW9wQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCEjBVqymzca1SIn3a5BW9wQ%2F&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=d4ab5c6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEjBVqymzca1SIn3a5BW9wQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n衝衝子 FA 升級攻略 - 槍傷系列 1：胸腔與腹部：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Jb-IysNZYcI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJb-IysNZYcI&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=6830a4a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Jb-IysNZYcI</a><br />\n<br />\n衝衝子 FA 升級攻略 - 槍傷系列 2： 四肢及頭部：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nad2Uyeyc58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fnad2Uyeyc58&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=74807e7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nad2Uyeyc58</a><br />\n<br />\n衝衝子 FA 升級攻略 - 撞車、骨折、外出血處理、止血帶及燒傷處理：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HVSvszCtJAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHVSvszCtJAc&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0